Cleanning CPU Type

data$Cpu_Type <- ''
data$Cpu_Series <- ''
data$Cpu_Speed <- ''
for (i in 1:nrow(data)){
  vec <- str_split(data$Cpu[i], ' ',simplify =TRUE)
  n <- length(vec)
  data$Cpu_Type[i] <- vec[1,1]
  data$Cpu_Speed[i] <- vec[1,n]
  n <- n-1
  temp <- vec[1,2]
  for (j in 3:n){
    temp <- paste(temp,vec[1,j])
  }
  data$Cpu_Series[i] <- temp
}
